Package org.cyclops.integratedcrafting.api.crafting

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ICraftingInterface
    A handler for invoking crafting recipes.
    ICraftingProcessOverride
    A certain override for performing a crafting process.
    ICraftingProcessOverrideRegistry
    A registry for ICraftingProcessOverride.
    ICraftingResultsSink
    A sink for crafting results from a ICraftingProcessOverride.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CraftingJob  
    CraftingJobDependencyGraph
    A CraftingJobDependencyGraph stores dependencies between crafting jobs based on their unique ID.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    CraftingJobStatus
    Status types for a CraftingJob in an ICraftingInterface.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    FailedCraftingRecipeException
    An exception for when a crafting recipe could not be crafted due to failing sub-dependencies.
    RecursiveCraftingRecipeException
    An exception for when an infinitely recursive crafting recipe was found.
    UnavailableCraftingInterfacesException
    An exception for when a crafting job could not be started due to no crafting interfaces being available.
    UnknownCraftingRecipeException
    An exception for when a crafting recipe for the given instance is unavailable.
